Title: Quasiperiodic fields and Bose-Einstein condensation
Authors: P. F. Borges, H. Boschi-Filho and C. Farina
Comments: Cover plus 9 Latex pages, no figures
\\
  We construct a partition function for fields obeying a quasiperiodic boundary
condition at finite temperature, $\psi(0;\vec x)= e^{i\theta} \psi(\beta;\vec
x)$, which interpolate continously that ones corresponding to bosons and
fermions and discuss the possibility of condensation for these fields.
